== 2015年：早期罢课 ==
{{See also|{{le|2015年全球气候游行|Global Climate March 2015}}}}
2006年11月，澳大利亚青年气候联盟（Australian Youth Climate Coalition）正式成立，开始组织有关气候变化的活动，吸引青年和学生参与<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.smh.com.au/environment/climate-change/climate-warriors-march-behind-little-green-book-20090710-dg2t.html|title=Climate warriors march behind little green book|first=Kelsey|last=Munro|date=2009-07-10|website=The Sydney Morning Herald|access-date=2020-10-26|archive-date=2016-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817175257/http://www.smh.com.au/environment/climate-change/climate-warriors-march-behind-little-green-book-20090710-dg2t.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2010年，气候营在英国多家发动罢课，呼吁民众关注气候变化<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.theguardian.com/environment/2011/mar/02/climate-camp-disbanded|title=Climate Camp disbanded|date=2011-03-02|website=the Guardian|access-date=2020-10-26|archive-date=2020-11-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201112032503/http://www.theguardian.com/environment/2011/mar/02/climate-camp-disbanded|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2015年11月底，有独立学生团体邀请全球其他学生在巴黎[[2015年联合国气候变化大会|2015年联合国气候变化大会]]首日罢课。11月30日，会议首日，全球共有100多个国家举行“气候大罢课”，约5万人参与<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0GjdVgGfcb8 |title=Climate Strike 2015: Students Skip School demanding Climate Actions |work=Climate Strike |date=2016-03-01 |access-date=2019-03-14 |publisher=YouTube |archive-date=2019-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190922063013/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0GjdVgGfcb8 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。运动主要有三个诉求：全面使用[[可持续能源|可持续能源]]、保留[[化石燃料|化石燃料]]、协助[[环境难民|环境难民]]<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.climatestrike.net/ |title=Climate Strike |website=climatestrike.net |access-date=2019-03-14 |archive-date=2020-02-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200228231528/https://www.climatestrike.net/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 2018年：格蕾塔·通贝里罢课 ==
[[File:Greta_Thunberg_4.jpg|thumb]]在[[瑞典议会|瑞典议会]]前]]
[[File:Old_town_Stockholm_the_bike_of_Greta.jpeg|thumb]]抗议者的自行车，上面的标语写着：“必须将全球变暖当成危机！气候是最重要的选举议题！”]]
2018年8月20日，经历了{{tsl|en|2018 European heat wave|2018年欧洲热浪|热浪}}和{{tsl|en|2018 Sweden wildfires|2018年瑞典大火|大火}}、当时还是[[九年级|九年级]]学生的瑞典气候活动人士[[格蕾塔·通贝里|格蕾塔·通贝里]]决定罢课，直至[[2018年瑞典大选|2018年瑞典大选]]举行的9月9日<ref name="John_CNN_20190213">{{Cite news |title=How teenage girls defied skeptics to build a new climate movement |date=2019-02-13 |author-first=Tara |author-last=John |publisher=CNN |url=https://edition.cnn.com/2019/02/13/uk/student-climate-strike-girls-gbr-scli-intl/index.html |access-date=2019-02-28 |dead-url=no |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190228102034/https://edition.cnn.com/2019/02/13/uk/student-climate-strike-girls-gbr-scli-intl/index.html |archive-date=2019-02-28 }}</ref><ref name="Crouch"/>，说自己是受到了美国[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]][[帕克兰_(佛罗里达州)|帕克兰]][[2018年佛罗里达校园枪击案|玛乔丽·斯通曼·道格拉斯高中]]的学生组织{{tsl|en|March for Our Lives|生命大游行}}的启发<ref>{{cite news |title=Teen activist on climate change: If we don't do anything right now, we're screwed |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rGmBkIUwYkA |access-date=2019-02-10 |agency=CNN |date=2018-12-23 |archive-date=2019-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190315172703/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rGmBkIUwYkA |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title=The Guardian view on teenage activists: protesters not puppets – Editorial |url=https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2019/feb/07/the-guardian-view-on-teenage-activists-look-whos-pulling-the-strings |access-date=2019-02-11 |newspaper=The Guardian |date=2019-02-07 |archive-date=2019-02-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190211043029/https://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2019/feb/07/the-guardian-view-on-teenage-activists-look-whos-pulling-the-strings |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

通贝里每天上学时间都会到[[瑞典议会|瑞典议会]]外静坐抗议，举着一张写着“气候大罢课”的标语<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.newyorker.com/news/our-columnists/the-fifteen-year-old-climate-activist-who-is-demanding-a-new-kind-of-politics |title=The Fifteen-Year-Old Climate Activist Who Is Demanding a New Kind of Politics |date=2018-10-02 |website=The New Yorker |access-date=2021-01-04 |archive-date=2019-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190105223945/https://www.newyorker.com/news/our-columnists/the-fifteen-year-old-climate-activist-who-is-demanding-a-new-kind-of-politics |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她的其中一个诉求是瑞典政府依照《[[巴黎协定|巴黎协定]]》减少[[温室气体|碳排放]]。9月7日，大选前夕，她宣布之后的每个星期五都会罢课，直到瑞典遵守《巴黎协定》。她创造了“週五為未來而戰”（FridaysForFuture）这一口号，受国际关注，激励全球的学生参与罢课<ref name="Guardian2">{{Cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2018/dec/04/leaders-like-children-school-strike-founder-greta-thunberg-tells-un-climate-summit |title='Our leaders are like children,' school strike founder tells climate summit |date=2018-12-04 |newspaper=The Guardian |accessdate=2021-01-04 |archive-date=2019-01-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190102050002/https://www.theguardian.com/environment/2018/dec/04/leaders-like-children-school-strike-founder-greta-thunberg-tells-un-climate-summit |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

之后，她展开为期两周的帆船航行，前往纽约，继续唤起大家共同应对气候危机。9月20日，她参与美国当地的罢课活动，9月23日在纽约的联合国气候变化大会上发言<ref>Tara Law. [https://time.com/5663534/greta-thunberg-arrives-sail-atlantic/ "Climate Activist Greta Thunberg Arrives in New York After Sailing Across the Atlantic"] {{Wayback|url=https://time.com/5663534/greta-thunberg-arrives-sail-atlantic/ |date=20191102100913 }}. TIME. (28 August 2019).</ref>。

