-000-swiss-pupils-strike-over-climate/44636034 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Gueissaz">{{Cite news |author-first=Rouven |author-last=Gueissaz |url=https://www.rts.ch/info/regions/autres-cantons/10091787-la-greve-du-climat-rassemble-des-centaines-d-etudiants-alemaniques.html |title=La "grève du climat" rassemble des centaines d'étudiants alémaniques |date=2018-12-22 |work=RTS Info |language=fr |quote=["Climate strike" brings together hundreds of German-speaking students] |accessdate=2021-01-04 |archive-date=2019-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191010203339/https://www.rts.ch/info/regions/autres-cantons/10091787-la-greve-du-climat-rassemble-des-centaines-d-etudiants-alemaniques.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>、英国和美国<ref name="Guardian2"/><ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.expressen.se/nyheter/klimat/klimatmanifestation-over-hela-landet-odesfraga/ |title=Klimatmanifestation över hela landet: "Ödesfråga" |date=2018-11-30 |newspaper=Expressen |language=sv |accessdate=2021-01-04 |archive-date=2019-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190831114644/https://www.expressen.se/nyheter/klimat/klimatmanifestation-over-hela-landet-odesfraga/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

