2019年1月31日，3400名比利时科学家和学者发表联署[[公开信|公开信]]，支持罢课行动<ref name="scientists4climate-be">{{cite web |url=https://scientists4climate.be/letter/english/ |title=Strengthen your climate ambitions! |author=Scientsts4Climate |date=2019-01-31 |access-date=2021-01-04 |archive-date=2019-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190926071459/https://scientists4climate.be/letter/english/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。信件表示：“依气候学的事实看来，活动家们是正确的，这也是为什么我们科学家会支持他们”<ref name="vrtnws-2019">{{cite news |url=https://www.vrt.be/vrtnws/nl/2019/01/30/3-300-belgische-wetenschappers-zetten-feiten-op-een-rijtje-in-op/ |title=Meer dan 3.400 wetenschappers zetten feiten op een rij in open brief: "Klimaatbetogers hebben groot gelijk" |date=2019-01-31 |access-date=2019-01-31 |publisher=vrtnws |website=www.vrt.be |archive-date=2019-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414130035/https://www.vrt.be/vrtnws/nl/2019/01/30/3-300-belgische-wetenschappers-zetten-feiten-op-een-rijtje-in-op/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。随后，340名荷兰科学家联署支持当地的罢课<ref name="dutchnews-2019">{{cite news |url=https://www.dutchnews.nl/news/2019/02/350-scientists-back-dutch-school-kids-climate-demonstration/ |title=350 scientists back Dutch school kids climate demonstration |date=2019-02-07 |access-date=2019-02-09 |publisher=DutchNews |website=DutchNews.nl |archive-date=2019-02-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190209180349/https://www.dutchnews.nl/news/2019/02/350-scientists-back-dutch-school-kids-climate-demonstration/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年3月11日，1200名荷兰研究人员联署支持罢课<ref>{{cite web |url=https://yle.fi/uutiset/3-10683192 |title=Yli 1200 tutkijaa tukee ilmastolakkoilevia nuoria: "Planeetan hyväksikäyttö on lastemme laiminlyöntiä" |website=Yle.fi |access-date=2019-03-14 |archive-date=2019-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190327233506/https://yle.fi/uutiset/3-10683192 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2019年3月，《[[自然_(期刊)|自然]]》刊发文章，列出科学界其他人对气候罢课行动的支持，态度清一色支持，无批评之言。其中一条评论认为，“气候罢课的观点是革命性、前所未见的。我认为，这是非暴力公民抗命运动的正确形式”<ref name="Warren2019">{{cite journal |author-last=Warren |author-first=Matthew |title=Thousands of scientists are backing the kids striking for climate change |journal=Nature |volume=567 |issue=7748 |date=2019 |pages=291–292 |issn=0028-0836 |doi=10.1038/d41586-019-00861-z|pmid=30890800 |bibcode=2019Natur.567..291W |doi-access=free }}</ref>。

