020-10-26|archive-date=2020-08-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200804003425/https://www.edie.net/news/11/How-have-key-MPs-responded-to-Greta-Thunberg-and-the-climate-protests-/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite tweet|user=jeremycorbyn|last=Corbyn|first=Jeremy|number=1096358314743685120|date=2019-02-15|title=Climate change is the greatest threat that we all face but it is the school kids of today whose futures are most on the line. They are right to feel let down by the generation before them and it’s inspiring to see them making their voice heard today.#SchoolStrike4Climate}}</ref><ref>{{Cite tweet|user=jeremycorbyn|last=Corbyn|first=Jeremy|number=1116710295467188229|date=2019-04-12|
