澳大利亚总理[[斯科特·莫里森|斯科特·莫里森]]呼吁学生“多学习，少出来行动”<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.news.com.au/technology/environment/climate-change/why-scott-morrison-is-worse-than-tony-abbott/news-story/ac9c3a43a0097e668b5e4ab4406bcb4a |title=Scott Morrison, student climate strike: PM calls for 'less activism in schools' |website=www.news.com.au |access-date=2019-03-16 |archive-date=2019-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190316095952/https://www.news.com.au/technology/environment/climate-change/why-scott-morrison-is-worse-than-tony-abbott/news-story/ac9c3a43a0097e668b5e4ab4406bcb4a |dead-url=no }}</ref>。教育部长[[丹·特漢|丹·特漢]]表示，如果学生们认为这个议题非常重要，应该在放学后或者周末行动<ref name="ReutersVoldemort">{{Cite web |url=https://www.reuters.com/article/us-climate-change-youth-idUSKCN1QW01S |title='Worse than Voldemort': Global students' strike targets climate change |date=2019-03-15 |via=www.reuters.com |access-date=2021-01-04 |archive-date=2019-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190318213908/https://www.reuters.com/article/us-climate-change-youth-idUSKCN1QW01S |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

